{"tid":479051,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[秒回毒拎樹窿] 今星期覺得灰既事","createTime":"2017-11-24T16:21:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-25T20:31:42.000Z","uid":62225,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"50047345081ff1a0284298a302a68ec8dbe3fa03","tid":479051,"uid":62225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T16:21:03.000Z","msg":"今星期試下唔好感情事，真心想聽下大家今星期發生左d 咩事。<br />\n<br />\n『唔講男朋友今星期對你做左乜，唔講你覺得女朋友今星期點。』<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4512432c6cbf3eb9fd6cdb70fc447e0066ac03bb","tid":479051,"uid":65256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T16:22:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">now<br />\n隻手瘀左好撚痛</span></span>"},{"pid":"09ee0c8371e3c7c0aff701f504502509d8041983","tid":479051,"uid":127116,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T16:33:34.000Z","msg":"覺得自己係一個可有可無既閒雜人等"},{"pid":"5cf11c6382eeefb5f5deb42149e7e6e5dac44a37","tid":479051,"uid":62225,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T16:35:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">now<br />\n隻手瘀左好撚痛</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解瘀左嫁 你打人呀"},{"pid":"b3ea30f4ef7d7800457c38a994b488b2586cb0c1","tid":479051,"uid":62225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T16:35:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>覺得自己係一個可有可無既閒雜人等</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想知，再講多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1584ab17626ecc1edc193c01fe6f292e8881533","tid":479051,"uid":127116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T16:40:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>覺得自己係一個可有可無既閒雜人等</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想知，再講多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n返工成日無野做<br />\n有時覺得有啲工作自己都勝任到<br />\n但未有機會表現出來無人知<br />\n有時就覺得自己好廢連少少野都做得唔好<br />\n<br />\n最重要係搵極都搵唔到人生目標<br />\n變左條咸魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連自己想做咩都唔知<br />\n為返工而返工"},{"pid":"754656a7b7b63bb72bdbc43e91e84ba99fd1c7fc","tid":479051,"uid":136637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T16:41:15.000Z","msg":"扭親隻腳 可能好耐都冇得跳舞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇得跳舞嘅生活係黑白嘅"},{"pid":"6f63f3883cbcf6c4890d21e485f50e388eb82caa","tid":479051,"uid":62225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T16:42:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>覺得自己係一個可有可無既閒雜人等</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想知，再講多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n返工成日無野做<br />\n有時覺得有啲工作自己都勝任到<br />\n但未有機會表現出來無人知<br />\n有時就覺得自己好廢連少少野都做得唔好<br />\n<br />\n最重要係搵極都搵唔到人生目標<br />\n變左條咸魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連自己想做咩都唔知<br />\n為返工而返工</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唉，係呀，番工明明自己識做個d 野，完全無人搵自己做。做左小小野幫到件事，又無人會欣賞。真係長期會灰。<br />\n<br />\n會唔會試下搵d 興趣班玩下去讀下咁呀，or 做義工個d？？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n巴打幾多歲？？"},{"pid":"431d01543d42d845a6710b7f7f0f11ecb5a51cb9","tid":479051,"uid":62225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T16:42:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>扭親隻腳 可能好耐都冇得跳舞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇得跳舞嘅生活係黑白嘅</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絲打跳舞好勁？跳咩舞嫁？"},{"pid":"073b2ce950285916a7a15d5f84a916fed4abb59b","tid":479051,"uid":143908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T16:43:19.000Z","msg":"冇還書俾人罰成五六十蚊<img src=\"/asse